Document: EditorScenePostImport
Path: godot/classes/class_editorscenepostimport.rst
Summary: Provides tools to modify scene import settings after initial import in Godot.

Class: EditorScenePostImport
Inherits: EditorPlugin < EditorSceneImport

This class allows users to adjust scene import configurations after the initial import process. It provides functionality for modifying import settings through the editor interface, including options for adjusting scene hierarchy, material assignments, and node properties. The class handles post-import operations such as applying custom import rules, updating scene metadata, and ensuring consistency between imported assets and project settings. It works in conjunction with the EditorSceneImport class to complete the scene import workflow.
