Document: EditorScenePostImport
Path: godot/classes/class_editorscenepostimport.rst
Summary: Core methods for handling scene post-import operations and retrieving source file information.

- _post_import (Node scene): Virtual method called after scene import. Must return modified scene version.
- get_source_file (): Constant method returning source file path (e.g. res://scene.dae)

Note: _post_import must return the modified version of the scene after import operations. 
Note: get_source_file provides the original file path used for importing the scene.